data.description: Come check out one of the largest homes in the neighborhood! With 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths. The extra large great room and living space on the second floor provide PLENTY of space for the family! Granite counters in kitchen. Large backyard with privacy fence that is a perfect entertaining area even has 2 entry points for convenience. Recent updates include new garage doors and openers, fresh paint (2023), a french drain installed in the backyard (2020), ceiling fans with lights added to 3 bedrooms(2020) and Kitchen (2023), a new dishwasher, and a newer microwave. Hardwood floors were recently refinished. Conveniently located near Town Center and Mount Trashmore, bases and interstates. Come check this gorgeous home out!
